Package: AlphaGenomeR
Title: R Interface to Google DeepMind's AlphaGenome API
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: person("Himanshu", "Bhandary", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "2032ushimanshu@gmail.com",
    comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-9859-3934"))
Description: Provides an R interface to the AlphaGenome API by Google DeepMind.
    AlphaGenome offers multimodal predictions including gene expression,
    splicing patterns, chromatin features, and contact maps for genomic regions.
    This package bridges the official Python SDK using reticulate to handle
    gRPC communication, allowing R users to seamlessly integrate AlphaGenome
    predictions into genomic analysis workflows.
